\nfermions, which can be searched for in $e^+ e^- \\to \\text{hadrons +\ninvisibles}$ at Belle II and BESIII. Due to the low new physics scale dark\nfermions can easily induce an early Landau pole, requiring models to be\nUV-completed near the TeV-scale.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Oct 2022 18:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Nov 2022 20:11:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-10"}
