s is shown to be skillful in filtering\nnonlinear turbulent flow fields with strong non-Gaussian features.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Oct 2022 23:12:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 May 2023 09:25:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-10"}
